Chicago Bulls Defeat Hawks 99-82 to Take 2-1 Lead in NBA Playoff Series

-- B y   N a n c y   K e r c h e v a l
-- 
2011-05-07T01:38:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-07/chicago-bulls-defeat-hawks-99-82-to-take-2-1-lead-in-nba-playoff-series.html
The  Chicago Bulls  defeated the Atlanta
Hawks 99-82 to take a 2-1 lead in the National Basketball
Association playoff series.
 Derrick Rose  scored 44 points for the Bulls at Philips Arena in
Atlanta. Jeff Teague had 21 points for the Hawks.  Atlanta hosts Game 4 on May 8 in the best-of-seven series.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nancy Kercheval at 
 nkercheval@bloomberg.net  